#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet.rst:35
msgid "The Spreadsheet module is part of **Odoo Documents**."
msgstr "Le module Spreadsheet fait partie d'**Odoo Documents**."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet.rst:38
msgid ""
"Odoo spreadsheets serve as the foundation for the :doc:`dashboards available "
"in Odoo Dashboards <../../applications/productivity/dashboards>`. On a "
"dashboard, charts and data tables are used to display dynamic Odoo data and "
"provide an overview of key business metrics."
msgstr ""
"Les feuilles de calcul Odoo servent de base aux :doc:`tableaux de bord "
"disponibles dans Odoo Tableaux de bord <../../applications/productivity/"
"dashboards>`. Sur un tableau de bord, les graphiques et tableaux de données "
"sont utilisés pour afficher des données Odoo dynamiques et fournir un aperçu "
"des indicateurs métier clés."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet.rst:42
msgid ""
":ref:`Standard, pre-configured dashboards <dashboards/consult-dashboards/"
"standard>` can be :ref:`customized <build_and_customize_dashboards/"
"customize>` by editing the dashboard's underlying spreadsheet via "
"Dashboards. :ref:`Custom dashboards <build_and_customize_dashboards/build>` "
"can also be created from scratch, starting from an Odoo spreadsheet; any "
"subsequent :ref:`modifications <build_and_customize_dashboards/customize>` "
"are performed via Dashboards."
msgstr ""
"Les :ref:`tableaux de bord standard pré-configurés <dashboards/consult-"
"dashboards/standard>` peuvent être :ref:`personnalisés "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/customize>` en modifiant la feuille de "
"calcul sous-jacente du tableau de bord via Tableaux de bord. Des "
":ref:`tableaux de bord personnalisés <build_and_customize_dashboards/build>` "
"peuvent également être créés à partir de zéro, en partant d'une feuille de "
"calcul Odoo ; toute :ref:`modification <build_and_customize_dashboards/"
"customize>` ultérieure est effectuée via Tableaux de bord."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/get_started.rst:3
